    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Hard, red, scented wood of the species Prunus mahaleb, used for small objects such as nutcrackers and tobacco rasps.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
